snippet.title: Spram's Metroid Doom
snippet.description:
Almost done.

A lot of graphics from Metroid games, Metal Gear Solid and Phantasy Star 4 among others. Music taken from vgmusic.com

Samus' arm cannon was taken from an image I found that I thought was Metroid Prime's but was actually done by someone else as part of another mod for another game. Sorry!
